overview: When chess club co-captain Lana Rhoades comes to town, she reunites with co-captain August Ames over their annual game of chess. Agency owner Angela White suggests that her personal assistant Keisha Grey has a promising future in modeling if she plays her cards right. Darcie Dolce oddly requests that her new housekeeper April O'Neil wears a French maid costume while she cleans. Tarot-reading MILF Jelena Jensen resorts to voodoo to help he distraught friend Angela White after she discovered that her husband is cheating.
title: Naturally Stacked Stories
